column5: Does anyone have any info on LeBron's Camp? It's located north of Sioux Narrows on the west side of the highway just before the Reed Narrows bridge. I clicked on the website and it said the domain was for sale.
a quick google search came up with it being closed permanetly.
maybe after he retires from basketball he will reopen it.....
Not sure he can afford to re-open it!
It is closed and was turned into an AirBNB.
